{"tid":2253584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國學運出現重大隱憂 保皇黨大集結揚言反制！","createTime":"2020-10-22T08:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T11:56:35.000Z","uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2d98c6a28097e71eeeef8e8f96b875bd65f82a39","tid":2253584,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:57:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">泰國上議院主席蓬佩攜眾表達保皇立場！</span></strong><br />\n2020年10月22日 - by 知否<br />\nSHARETWEETSHARE<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20201022140107-735x400.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%259B%25BE%25E7%2589%2587_20201022140107-735x400.png&h=6f4ad6af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰國頭條新聞社訊 據泰媒報導，10月22日泰國上議院主席蓬佩攜眾議員、公務員一起表達保皇立場，並強調上議院議員遵守憲法規定履行職責。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，<span class=\"red\">今天上議院主席蓬佩攜上議院議員、公務員、工作人員等身穿黃色服飾、手持國旗和王室旗幟站在國王肖像前唱著歌，並宣誓以表達維護王室的立場！</span><br />\n<br />\n蓬佩表示，上議院議員的立場是：通過議員遵照憲法第2、3條規定使用民主權利的職責來保衛王室，可能會有人對上議院議員職責角色理解模糊，所以今天攜各方出來表明上議院議員的職責角色，同時也是一種提醒在上議院議員履職時。他相信過去一年中，上議院議員都了解到議員本身的職責，並且會繼續工作下去。 （來源於Tna,編譯：知否）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20201022140102.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%259B%25BE%25E7%2589%2587_20201022140102.png&h=17966ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thaiheadlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20201022140104.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thaiheadlines.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%259B%25BE%25E7%2589%2587_20201022140104.png&h=d1f96349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"h