itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:11:35.000Z","msg":"啲廢老都就死啦, 仲要阻住地球轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c973357420d60db76f217a73fc90cab6a7cb29c","tid":2253584,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:12:44.000Z","msg":"到時會唔會有泰國四眼仔叫人唔好打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c004b3f927630a73296efdb5b4385497091b1133","tid":2253584,"uid":378294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:13:12.000Z","msg":"依家泰國黃衫軍=以前紅衫軍+黃衫軍"},{"pid":"89dec01aef465417a6151f1781e3ae9fc54075d1","tid":2253584,"uid":51620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c545a84ec2d0d27f3db5ec8486342f42b082e7f9","tid":2253584,"uid":62749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:02:39.000Z","msg":"泰國藍屍出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但人地着黃衫 真保皇(泰皇)"},{"pid":"c9810ccfb97f56a9b72021e5195c164167c8492b","tid":2253584,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:17:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">泰保皇派也不甩禁令上街集會 高舉國王肖像護君主制</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/21/phpOfhWcD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F21%2FphpOfhWcD.jpg&h=2bceae90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰國保皇黨數今（21）日在曼谷等各地區走上街頭，稱他們的聚會不具政治性，因此不受政府集會禁令所限制。（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n2020/10/21 19:26<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">面對成千上萬人參與的反政府和訴求改革君主制示威活動持續延燒，泰國保皇黨數今（21）日也在曼谷等各地區走上街頭，稱他們的聚會不具政治性，因此不受政府集會禁令所限制。</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，在反政府抗議團體敦促支持者今日下午4時聚集，進行連續第7天的遊行示威之際，保皇派也走上街頭，呼籲抗議者要求前軍事將領、現任總理帕拉育（Prayut Chan-o-cha）沒問題，但不應該扯上國王瓦吉拉隆功。<br />\n<br />\n保皇黨人士、24歲的西里蒙哥（Sirimongkol Ruampan）表示，「我求求你，做你想做的，但不要觸動君主制。」他說，「我不相信暴力。我再次祈求，不要將君主制帶入政治。」<br />\n<br />\n保皇派人士大多數都穿著代表支持王室的黃色衣服，並表示他們的聚會不具政治性，因此不受政府上週起禁止5人以上集會的限制。但警方表示，他們對所有團體一視同仁。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">外媒指出，保皇黨數十人週三在曼谷蘭甘亨大學（Rankhamhaeng University）聚集支持瓦吉拉隆功的君主專制政府時，與反政府人士發生衝突，雙方互相叫罵，有人扔出水瓶和其他物品。</span><br />\n<br />\n警方說，他們正試圖將這些團體分開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3328258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3328258&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=bd5ce6f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3328258&h=e1842df9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3328258</a>"},{"pid":"86e2d8269c9cbf27b4a393fb583b1a135bd9aaee","tid":2253584,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rrzCS24BR8l7Lv788An3zA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9MzU0/https://media.zenfs.com/en/cna.com.tw/01f5ef105cdd31c290f11a47d939dcdc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FrrzCS24BR8l7Lv788An3zA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9MzU0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fcna.com.tw%2F01f5ef105cdd31c290f11a47d939dcdc&h=87b2cd0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d062f59f022eb0a043db119a07e51b4e9568f41a","tid":2253584,"uid":7849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:23:48.000Z","msg":"21世紀都依然有人希望做奴才"},{"pid":"de55c577851b3a3eabef059b35ad57eef794e744","tid":2253584,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsimg.ftv.com.tw/summernotefiles/News/6efdd15d-1a34-4233-b2ae-e7a14e49b51f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.ftv.com.tw%2Fsummernotefiles%2FNews%2F6efdd15d-1a34-4233-b2ae-e7a14e49b51f.jpg&h=d9338226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此次泰人抗議，也發展出一套躲避警方的暗號來溝通，舉例來說，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">摩卡咖啡代表著警察</span></span>；<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">咖啡是水砲車</span></span>；<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">冰黑咖啡是鎮暴警察</span></span>；<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">泰式辣咖哩是誤導警方的意思</span></span>；<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">藍色小精靈代表被添加顏色的水柱噴灑到的示威者</span></span>；<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">紅蘿蔔是僧人</span></span>；<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">小小兵則是保皇派</span></span>。"},{"pid":"2f4901dc3ee2ae8906129729f86bb5ae9bc017b0","tid":2253584,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:28:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">好快有721</span>"},{"pid":"982094226d68867afd538be629ac6845e79d49ae","tid":2253584,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:29:54.000Z","msg":"保皇黨.....歷史上好似冇咩邊個係好下場"},{"pid":"187ba2bc71cc847d9ee45d0aaf0c9e134c7b4fab","tid":2253584,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsimg.ftv.com.tw/summernotefiles/News/ee6d3dbb-1c1f-4d66-9341-fb4e7dad0f4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.ftv.com.tw%2Fsummernotefiles%2FNews%2Fee6d3dbb-1c1f-4d66-9341-fb4e7dad0f4b.jpg&h=6ca4cc89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n21日泰國各地就出現身穿代表君王顏色的黃衣人"},{"pid":"52b4da0a32d39cf508986553a4b1c60f38b11241","tid":2253584,"uid":50931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1c0f0ae1c3f9793326e87899809c4700d62de786","tid":2253584,"uid":89608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:58:27.000Z","msg":"睇黎好快會有流氓打人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:35:01.000Z","msg":"已經出過手"},{"pid":"e73db75fba29e320e9a73e1294800909232cd2c5","tid":2253584,"uid":60977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:35:47.000Z","msg":"仲擺普密篷係咩意思"},{"pid":"9e0e792661ce807d725471d2159ef798f38d89d8"